clone the project from github
git clone https://github.com/j-s-135/local-storage

run
uvicorn main:app --port 8080

upload
open upload.html in browser
choose file
type in file name
select "hash file name"
the file hash should appear in the text box - that will be the file name that is saved on the server
select >>> to upload the file

view the file in the uploads folder

download
open download.html in browser
type in the file name that you typed on the upload form
select "retrieve hash >>>"
the same hash from before should appear in the textbox
select >>> to download the file
